# Claude Code — user-local settings, credentials, and state (never commit).
# Team-shared files under .claude/ (settings.json, commands/, agents/, hooks.json,
# CLAUDE.md) remain tracked on purpose — only the user-local variants are ignored.
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/.credentials.json
**/.claude/*.local.json
